NK010(tha)015:0: phur pa rgyud lugs las byug bdug brab gsum gyi bsgrub tshul bzhugs /
NK010(tha)015:2: byug bdug brab gsum gyi rdzas bsgrub tshul la don gsum las /
NK010(tha)015:3: dang po nyung dkar la rdzas bsag pa dang /
NK010(tha)015:7: nyung dkar nang nas zur bzhi pa //
NK010(tha)015:8: phrin las rnam bzhi rdzogs pa'i rtags //
NK010(tha)015:9: pho mo gnyis kyi thod pa ru //
NK010(tha)015:10: go ro tsa na ma bral ba //
NK010(tha)015:11: thabs dang shes rab kha sbyor ba //
NK010(tha)015:12: b+han+d+ha'i spyi bo brtol ba ni //
NK010(tha)015:13: de yi nang du sa bzhag lud //
NK010(tha)015:14: ro bsregs pa yi thal chen dang //
NK010(tha)015:15: nyung dkar sa bon gsum du gsal //
NK010(tha)015:16: zhes pa ltar pho mo'i thod pa klad zhag dang
NK010(tha)015:17: ldan pa kha sbyar gyi pho thod brtol ba'i nang
NK010(tha)015:18: du ro thal bsres pa'i sa 'jam dang /
NK010(tha)015:19: bla ma yab yum mam sgrub po'i dri che chung /
NK010(tha)015:20: khrag chen bsres pa'i lud ran par bya ste /
NK010(tha)015:21: yab yum dri chen dur khrod sa //
NK010(tha)015:22: khrag chen chags pa'i sa bon bsres //
NK010(tha)015:24: de dar mthing nag gis bkab la /
NK010(tha)015:25: lam rgya gram mam shing gcig drung la sogs par ma d+hal gru bzhi'i steng bkod la /
NK010(tha)015:26: mchod pa'i bye brag kyang bsham mo //
NK010(tha)015:29: b+han+d+ha khang pa sa bon lha //
NK010(tha)015:30: bskyed dang spyan drang rim pas mchod //
NK010(tha)015:31: mtheb mdzub nyi zla'i dkyil 'khor bar //
NK010(tha)015:32: khro bo sngo nag mtshon cha 'dzin //
NK010(tha)015:33: thugs las thon thim skur brlabs nas //
NK010(tha)015:36: sgrub thabs bsdus pas bdag mdun mnyam bsgrub byas la mdun bskyed dmigs rnam phyed par bya /
NK010(tha)015:38: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya hril shag dz+wa la ni h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)015:41: bsnyen pa zhag bdun bzlas brjod bya //
NK010(tha)015:42: brgya mtshams stong mtshams mchod pa yi //
NK010(tha)015:43: chu lud du ni bran bzhin dbul //
NK010(tha)015:44: ting 'dzin sngags dang phrin las kyis //
NK010(tha)015:45: khyad par mchod pa bdud rtsi dang //
NK010(tha)015:46: phyag rgya'i mchod pa gzhung bzhin bya //
NK010(tha)015:47: 'bras bu ma smin bar du dbul //
NK010(tha)015:48: khyad par nyung dkar sbom por 'gyur //
NK010(tha)015:51: du ba rlangs dang me 'od dang //
NK010(tha)015:54: gal te 'bras bu ma smin bar du sgrub nus na /
NK010(tha)015:55: sa bon myu gur gyur pa dang //
NK010(tha)015:56: sgrub po'i g.yas su nye ba yi //
NK010(tha)015:57: gnas su mtho gsum mthur du brko //
NK010(tha)015:58: sa yi ro rnams bsal ba yi //
NK010(tha)015:59: dpyid zla ra ba'i nya la ni //
NK010(tha)015:60: bzang po'i mtshams su b+han+d+ha sba'o //
NK010(tha)015:61: zla ba ngo drug bar du ni //
NK010(tha)015:62: gsal gdab bzlas brjod bar mi gcad //
NK010(tha)015:63: ston zla tha chung nya la barda'o //
NK010(tha)015:64: rul dang bam sum ma shor bar //
NK010(tha)015:65: nyi grib mtshams su legs bskams nas //
NK010(tha)015:66: grub pa'i 'bras bu sran ma ma sha tsam //
NK010(tha)015:67: dgun zla ra ba'i nya la zhal dro dngos grub blangs //
NK010(tha)015:68: de yis bde gshegs thugs bskul zhing //
NK010(tha)015:69: sdang dgra gnod bgegs rdul du rlog /
NK010(tha)015:70: rnal 'byor lus sam mgul du gdags //
NK010(tha)015:71: rtag tu lus la bcings pa las //
NK010(tha)015:72: g.yel bar byas na mi rung ngo //
NK010(tha)015:73: zhes pas myu gu ma thon bar du dkyil 'khor du bsgrubs shing /
NK010(tha)015:74: thon nas lam rgya gram la sogs par sa'i ro lnga bsal la chu lud bran zhing /
NK010(tha)015:75: zla dus thems par bsgrub bo //
NK010(tha)015:77: nyung dkar rgyal po'i drag rdzas 'di //
NK010(tha)015:78: gsang sngags bargya'am stong du ni //
NK010(tha)015:79: dam bcas lus la bcangs gyur na //
NK010(tha)015:80: las dbang dag kyang bzlog 'gyur zhing //
NK010(tha)015:81: bar chod kyis kyang tshugs mi 'gyur //
NK010(tha)015:82: yid la dran pas smon lam btsan //
NK010(tha)015:83: rig 'dzin byang chub sa non cing //
NK010(tha)015:84: gang la mngags pa nus mthur 'gyur //
NK010(tha)015:86: gnyis pa gu gul sgrub tshul la rdzas bsag pa dang /
NK010(tha)015:87: sgrub pa dngos kyi dang po ni /
NK010(tha)015:89: gu gul sbyar bar 'dod pa yis //
NK010(tha)015:90: dur khrod chen po rab dben par //
NK010(tha)015:91: dpyid zla ra ba'i nya la 'jug /
NK010(tha)015:92: man+dala gru bzhi gcig byas te //
NK010(tha)015:93: ban glang can gyi b+han+d+ha bsham //
NK010(tha)015:94: r+aa mig nya 'og skra spu'i gzhob //
NK010(tha)015:95: khyi spyang phag pa'i dri chen dkar //
NK010(tha)015:96: skye'u sne'u 'bras bu ra dug lce ba dang //
NK010(tha)015:97: zir d+ha du ra dang lce pog mu zi khrag chen dang //
NK010(tha)015:99: dug gi me tog thang chu dang //
NK010(tha)015:100: 'ug pa'i mig dang khra yi klad //
NK010(tha)015:101: sbrang rtsi ske tshe gcan gzan sder mo rnams //
NK010(tha)015:102: nges par bsags te cha bsnyams la //
NK010(tha)015:103: ra phod lug phod bong reng byang chub sems kyis dran //
NK010(tha)015:104: tshon gyi skud pas dam bcings la //
NK010(tha)015:105: kha ral ma yi zhabs mas gril //
NK010(tha)015:106: tsan+d+ha me la dros par bsro //
NK010(tha)015:107: man+dala dbus su de bzhag la //
NK010(tha)015:108: ba su ta yi gzungs thag gdags //
NK010(tha)015:110: de'i ra phod lug phod bong reng gsum gyi dwangs
NK010(tha)015:111: mas bran pa ni zhal las shes par bya zhing
NK010(tha)015:112: kha ral ma ni bud med kha mang po'o //
NK010(tha)015:114: bdag gtso lha mo bee t+aa li //
NK010(tha)015:115: bsam gtan gsal bar rab bzhugs te //
NK010(tha)015:116: bee t+aa nag mo 'khor lo can //
NK010(tha)015:117: nyi ma h+aum dang ldan pa la //
NK010(tha)015:118: spyan drangs bstim mchod rim par bya //
NK010(tha)015:119: zhes pas bdag bskyed bsdus pa'i gzhung bsrangs la /
NK010(tha)015:120: bzlas pa la bab pa na gtso bo'i yum las
NK010(tha)015:121: 'khor lo rgyas 'debs ma gnyis pa 'khor lo dang
NK010(tha)015:122: kha t+w+aam bsnams pa zhig chad pa gu gul dang
NK010(tha)015:123: gnyis su med par bsgoms la bzlas pa bya ba
NK010(tha)015:124: dang lhan cig / de bzhin gshegs pa thams cad
NK010(tha)015:125: kyi mthu stobs dang nus mthu 'od zer gyi rnam
NK010(tha)015:126: par spyan drangs nas rdzas la bstim pa yin te
NK010(tha)015:127: dang lhan cig / / de nyid las /
NK010(tha)015:128: de nas bsnyen pa 'di bzlas te //
NK010(tha)015:129: ma grub bar du rgyun mi bcad //
NK010(tha)015:130: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK010(tha)015:131: d+hu p+aam bee t+aa li ma ku ta la pra ta la h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)015:132: dal med rgyun du bzlas par bya //
NK010(tha)015:135: rtags byung nas ni nges bsam ste //
NK010(tha)015:136: lha la mchod de thig le bya //
NK010(tha)015:137: des ni gzi byin 'thob par byed //
NK010(tha)015:138: lus la bcangs na gdon bgegs 'joms //
NK010(tha)015:139: dud btang dgra la bdug gyur na //
NK010(tha)015:141: rtags de mngon du byung nas ni //
NK010(tha)015:142: rul dang sungs dang ma bam par //
NK010(tha)015:143: ril bu byas te rnal 'byor bcangs //
NK010(tha)015:144: gu gul sbyar ma'i rdzas su gsungs //
NK010(tha)015:148: sun tri ka yi thang chu dang //
NK010(tha)015:149: mi khyi gnyis kyi dri ma dang //
NK010(tha)015:150: spyang ki la du rta phur mo //
NK010(tha)015:151: dme ba lnga dang za 'og dang //
NK010(tha)015:152: 'bob mtshungs mi gtsang sna tshogs dag /
NK010(tha)015:153: 'brong ru g.yas kyi nang du brub //
NK010(tha)015:154: lam po che yi bzhi mdo ru //
NK010(tha)015:155: sbra nag phub la zhag bdun du //
NK010(tha)015:156: gsang sngags bzlas la mchod pa dbul //
NK010(tha)015:158: khro bo rnams kyi sngon byung dran //
NK010(tha)015:159: grub rdzas sems bskyed yid dran gyis //
NK010(tha)015:160: sras mchog khro bo gzi mdangs bskyed //
NK010(tha)015:161: bar chad rkyen dang bral bar 'gyur //
NK010(tha)015:164: gsum pa rak+ta bsgrub pa la gnyis /
NK010(tha)015:170: chu gling gnas su 'dug nas ni //
NK010(tha)015:171: man+dala dmar po zla gam bya'o //
NK010(tha)015:172: dgun zla ra ba'i nya la 'jug /
NK010(tha)015:183: rak+ta sum cu rtsa drug sogs //
NK010(tha)015:184: de la sbyor ba'i rak+tasa bran //
NK010(tha)015:185: le brgan dar gyis kha bkab nas //
NK010(tha)015:186: seng ldeng me la drod bsros nas //
NK010(tha)015:187: man+dala dbus su de bzhin gnas //
NK010(tha)015:190: m+au la rak+ta rtsa yi khrag /
NK010(tha)015:191: rdo shing rtsi shing dmar po brgya //
NK010(tha)015:193: bsgral ba'i ma h+aa rak+ta stong //
NK010(tha)015:194: na chung mtshams dang ldan pa yi //
NK010(tha)015:195: b+han+d+ha'i nang du rdzas blugs la //
NK010(tha)015:196: mtshan ldan gzhon nu'i pad+mara bcas //
NK010(tha)015:198: spyir 'khor ba'i rgyu chags sdang gnyis lugs ldog tu
NK010(tha)015:199: dag pa'i rten 'brel du sman raka gi mchod pa
NK010(tha)015:200: bstan la / de las rak+ta'i sgra don la ngo bo'i skabs su chags pa dang /
NK010(tha)015:201: dngos po'i skabs su khrag chen /
NK010(tha)015:202: kha dog gi skabs su dmar po la 'jug pa las /
NK010(tha)015:203: ma rig pa nas rga shi'i bar gyi rten 'brel lugs 'byung du rdzogs pa'i snying khrag dang /
NK010(tha)015:204: srog pa rtsa'i khrag la m+au la rak+ta zhes brjod de /
NK010(tha)015:205: chu dang ma 'dres dwangs ma'i khrag /
NK010(tha)015:207: rigs kyi rak+ta ni dung can ma la sogs pa'i rdul gyi thog ma ste pad+ma rak+ta'o //
NK010(tha)015:208: bsgral ba'i rak+ta ni zhing bcu bsgral ba'i khrag go //
NK010(tha)015:209: de ltar bzhi po rtsa bar byas pa'i steng du /
NK010(tha)015:210: yan lag rak+ta brtan pa'i khrag /
NK010(tha)015:213: de bzhin du 'khor ba rgyu'i rak+ta khrag sna tshogs tshad dang /
NK010(tha)015:214: srid pa gzhi'i rak+ta lte ba'i khrag dang /
NK010(tha)015:215: khrag thams cad kyi ngo bo nyid chu sna dang /
NK010(tha)015:216: snang ba brda'i rak+ta kha dog dmar por gyur tshad dang /
NK010(tha)015:217: na chung gi pad+ma'i ze 'bru rnams la sngon he
NK010(tha)015:218: ru kas r+au dra bsgral ba'i tshe khrag gi thig
NK010(tha)015:219: pa sa la ltung ba las byung ba'i snod kyi
NK010(tha)015:220: rak+ta lnga tshan lnga'i skyobs sbyar ba'i tshul la rdo'i
NK010(tha)015:221: rak+ta lnga ni / mtshal dang ldod ros btsag dang ni //
NK010(tha)015:222: mdud rtse sbal rgyab rnam pa lnga //
NK010(tha)015:225: rgya skag btsod dang seng ldeng dang //
NK010(tha)015:226: btsan dug thar nu rnam pa lnga //
NK010(tha)015:229: gla rtsi go che bu ram dang //
NK010(tha)015:230: 'bri smug sbrang rtsi rnam pa lnga //
NK010(tha)015:234: ra gag dmar po nas nag lnga //
NK010(tha)015:237: ug chos lug ru smug po dang //
NK010(tha)015:238: sran ma rgya lcam ram bu lnga //
NK010(tha)015:240: de ltar so lnga po btags te khrag chen gyis
NK010(tha)015:241: brus ril bur dril te bud med pad+ma can gyi
NK010(tha)015:242: b+han+d+hara bstsal la / dar dmar gyis kha gcad /
NK010(tha)015:243: seng lding gi me la ran par bsres te /
NK010(tha)015:244: man+dala gyi dbus su khri'i steng bzhag go //
NK010(tha)015:246: bdag gsal chags pa'i dbang can bsam //
NK010(tha)015:247: dgug bstim mnyes mchod bsnyen pa bzlas //
NK010(tha)015:249: bdag mdun bsgrub tshul snga ma bzhin la /
NK010(tha)015:251: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya ma h+aa rak+ta r+aa ga sa ma ya bu bu s+w+aa h+aa /
NK010(tha)015:253: mngon du khol lam rlangs pa 'byung //
NK010(tha)015:254: yang na lud dam 'phags na ni //
NK010(tha)015:255: lha la mchod de bdag nyid btung //
NK010(tha)015:256: chags pa bskyed cing mdangs kyang dmar //
NK010(tha)015:257: khams gsum mo yi pad+ma'i mdangs //
NK010(tha)015:261: bsnyen pa zhag bdun bar du ni //
NK010(tha)015:262: skyes pa dar ma'i rdo rje yis //
NK010(tha)015:263: dkrug cing gsang sngags rgyun du bzlas //
NK010(tha)015:265: rak+ta khol ma'i rtags dbyung ste //
NK010(tha)015:266: rnal 'byor rnams la rgyan btab na //
NK010(tha)015:267: dngos grub myur du thob par 'gyur //
NK010(tha)015:268: lha srin rnams kyang bran du khol //
NK010(tha)015:269: ma mo mkha' 'gro dbang du sdud //
NK010(tha)015:270: dngos grub sgrub la bar mi gcod //
NK010(tha)015:271: sras mchog rnams kyang de bzhin du //
NK010(tha)015:272: thugs dam rjes dran gzi mdangs bskyed //
NK010(tha)015:273: gang la nus mthu mthar phyin pa'i //
NK010(tha)015:274: dbang dang bsdu ba'i rdzas drag ste //
NK010(tha)015:277: gal te so so nas sgrub pa'i spros pa ma
NK010(tha)015:278: lcogs na gsum ka'i rdzas tshogs par byas la thod
NK010(tha)015:279: pa gsum du blugs nas cig car du bsgrubs kyang
NK010(tha)015:280: rung ste / rdo rje khros pa las /
NK010(tha)015:281: nyung dkar gu gul rak+ta gsum //
NK010(tha)015:282: mtshan ma ngan pa'i thod pa ru //
NK010(tha)015:283: gsum po so sor blug byas la //
NK010(tha)015:284: tsher ma'i shing gis kha bcad la //
NK010(tha)015:285: dkar nag sbra ni phub byas la //
NK010(tha)015:286: lam po che yi rgya gram du //
NK010(tha)015:287: ma grub bar du de bzhin bya //
NK010(tha)015:288: gzhan yang gru gsum mthing nag bsgom //
NK010(tha)015:289: badz+ra k+ai li k+ai la ya /
NK010(tha)015:290: hril shag dza la ni h+aum phata /
NK010(tha)015:291: du ba rlangs dang me 'od dang //
NK010(tha)015:293: de bzhin rtags la phebs pa dang //
NK010(tha)015:294: nyung dkar dbang po sna lngar brab //
NK010(tha)015:295: dri chen dri chu rkyen las bskyed //
NK010(tha)015:296: bdud kyi nyi ma bkra mi shis //
NK010(tha)015:297: ngan pa'i dus su 'di dag bsgrub //
